{
  "stem": "13313.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And unfortunately, if fell over the bridge onto the track.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was afraid to go home because I lost my cap on the day of liberation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] This I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] The psychology of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we're liberated, but nothing happens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a week goes by, two weeks go by.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Roggemans say, well, your parents are gone, and we have no more use for you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we'll start looking for an orphanage to  put you in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had no interest in keeping us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was-- we were gonna-- supposed to be in an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was going to be our fate after the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "About two and and a half weeks after this, she started to inquire about orphanages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'm standing in front of our little bedroom window, and all of a sudden I see my father and mother in front of the house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I can tell you that I-- if there was an Olympic record for, for, for running down the stairs, I must have broken it then.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] The reason it took so long was that there was no transportation, plus chaos.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Troops went through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The camp where my mother was liberated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My father was-- came out of hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He managed to survive in that same place where  my mother was in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother's camp was liberated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The German's abandoned it the day before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So everybody was let loose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My father was on foot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We're talking here about 20 miles maybe, on foot, went to that camp, found my mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then they found-- and then somehow on foot, they came-- they came to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that was the liberation.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
